swingle tree blight
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a trampled appearance of potatoes, caused by being trodden on by horses during moulding.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
